'''StarLiners''' was a successful company located in the [[Brak sector/Legends|Brak sector]]. It provided transport for individuals throughout the sector in the form of several passenger liners. It was founded by [[Fae Kalena]] during the reign of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] where it reached the height of its success and became the foremost passenger transport company in the entire sector.

